    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udcbc $17,000 - A smart, budget-friendly choice for the practical driver! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 a used car that shows the normal signs of everyday driving and may benefit from some minor attention here and there, but is fundamentally sound and ready to get you where you need to go. The exterior has some light wear and cosmetic blemishes consistent with its age, and the interior is functional and comfortable. If you're looking for reliable, no-frills transportation at an honest price, this could be the one for you! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid and dependable \u2014 this vehicle is in genuinely good condition and ready to serve its next owner well! The exterior looks great with only the minor signs of everyday use you'd expect from a car that's been driven and enjoyed. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with normal wear on high-touch areas but nothing that detracts from the overall experience. Mechanically, this car runs well and has been maintained, making it a reliable choice for daily driving. No major issues to hide here \u2014 just an honest, capable vehicle at a fair price!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptional find on the used market that rivals a brand-new purchase in nearly every way. The exterior is pristine, free of any scratches, dents, or paint imperfections, with a deep, glossy finish that turns heads. The interior is equally immaculate, showing no signs of wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or trim \u2014 everything looks and feels fresh from the factory. Mechanically, this car is in top-notch shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function perfectly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises to report. Tires have excellent tread remaining, brakes are responsive and strong, and all electronics, climate controls, and safety features operate flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that genuinely feels new \u2014 ideal for a buyer who demands the best without paying new-car prices.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "What a rare find \u2014 this is truly an exceptional vehicle in mint condition! This car looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a spotless interior, gleaming exterior free of scratches or blemishes, and a powertrain that purrs with precision. Every system is functioning flawlessly, and the attention to care this car has received is immediately evident the moment you step inside. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can be genuinely proud of, this is it \u2014 don't miss your chance!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what you're purchasing. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a reasonable shine with only minor surface scratches and light swirl marks visible under direct sunlight. There are no significant dents or rust concerns, though a couple of small door dings are present that are typical for a vehicle of this age. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing normal wear \u2014 no tears or major staining, though some light fading on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and armrests. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained with regular servicing; all major systems are in good working order. The tires have adequate tread remaining, and brakes are in acceptable condition. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that will serve a buyer well in everyday use, without the premium cost of a mint-condition car.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 an honest designation that we do not apply lightly, and one that reflects a car with significant mechanical and cosmetic issues that any prospective buyer must fully understand before purchasing. The exterior shows heavy wear throughout: the paint is faded, scratched, and chipped in multiple areas, with visible rust forming on the body panels and wheel wells. Dents and dings are present across the doors and quarter panels, and the trim pieces are cracked or missing in several spots. The interior is similarly worn \u2014 the upholstery is torn and stained, the dashboard has cracks, and several of the controls and features may not function as intended. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention; it may start and move under its own power, but it should not be considered reliable transportation without a thorough inspection and likely substantial repair work. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or seeking a parts vehicle. We strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a qualified mechanic. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, no hidden details.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    }
  ],
